**What was done:**
- Resolved P2 tech-debt: "Hero image inconsistency — pricing and about pages share the same unrelated crop"
- **Finding:** The debt entry was inaccurate — neither page actually had a `floatingImage` set. Both used `alignment="center"` which suppresses the floating image anyway, so they had no hero imagery at all compared to home/products pages.
- **Fix:** Added `floatingImage` + `alignment="left"` to both pages:
  - `pricing` → `/images/app-on-desktop.png`
  - `about` → `/images/teacher-at-board.png`
- Build passes, 35 tests pass
- Commits pushed: `4005e35` (fix), `3a64d26` (output log)

**New lesson added:** Always verify tech-debt descriptions against current code before implementing — descriptions can be outdated or wrong.
